{"tid":2217982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國深圳研究院招志願者模擬失重效應 臥床15天賺1.5萬 ！","createTime":"2020-09-26T01:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T04:08:18.000Z","uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d75b83f0b8fd2e36393c62070d8f131be65b84cd","tid":2217982,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71949c5f0b61c88e40b5752109059addf06a00b7","tid":2217982,"uid":65091,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:16:18.000Z","msg":"做完實驗臥床唔止15天<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6695119f58f4205db0dc8a79744a0b58cc545b64","tid":2217982,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:16:43.000Z","msg":"深圳的綠航星際太空科技研究院近日招募志願者，參與為期15天負6度頭低位臥床實驗，並承諾在實驗完成後支付1.5萬元人民幣報酬，吸引不少民眾報名。<br />\n<br />\n據招募資料顯示，實驗時間全長約35天，包括實驗前適應期、15天臥床及臥床後恢復期。初期會出現頭脹、頭暈、鼻塞等症狀，起床後初期會出現不能長時間站立等症狀，但一般在一周左右可恢復。<br />\n<br />\n志願者基本要求為男性，18至50歲，高中以上學歷，身體健康，不吸煙；身高160至175厘米，體重50至80公斤；具有較好的與人交流和溝通能力，能用普通話與人溝通交流；具有良好的心理素質和意志力；無臨床疾病無精神類疾病無犯罪記錄。<br />\n<br />\n負責人陳穎表示，在15天的臥床過程中，志願者吃喝拉撒都要躺在床上，會有護士照料，膳食也會有營養師進行指導。截至目前已經有約800人次報名。報名的志願者將需接受兩次臨床體檢及病理篩查，結果將在10月中下旬確定，只會選擇24人。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，大量的實驗研究表明，負6度頭低位臥床是目前最為廣泛的人體模擬失重效應的方法。在地面開展模擬失重生理效應與防護技術研究，對保障人類進駐太空，及發展大眾健康促進技術具有重要意義。NASA的科學家們可利用臥床實驗的研究結果，研究人體如何適應失重狀態，從而制定出有助於太空人執行任務的對抗措施。"},{"pid":"a512cde33b3f1a48840e5ccbd3107856eea59ae9","tid":2217982,"uid":63113,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oCCq1nf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoCCq1nf.png&h=8f688843&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89CbctW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89CbctW.png&h=b7799c0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iuekQfE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiuekQfE.gif&h=62ea59db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e256823207f58b4cda1bca3ad64542e83e011e4","tid":2217982,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:20:11.000Z","msg":"外國都有<br />\n不過支那特別信唔過"},{"pid":"686d6bc7f2f24a1bd96c8b20db0bfb41868f7bbb","tid":2217982,"uid":59522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:21:00.000Z","msg":"萬五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一千蚊日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c33ddaf9ab1f019de7108d81872abfeeb213fc9","tid":2217982,"uid":182927,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:26:39.000Z","msg":"得800人次報名你就知係假"},{"pid":"7ed26353212438b39e74e327d354e13c7073fd9b","tid":2217982,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:31:34.000Z","msg":"做完之後攞唔攞到錢都成問題"},{"pid":"2c26da547958229c419d3c2cfba10840306805f1","tid":2217982,"uid":248299,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:34:52.000Z","msg":"咁先得果15k<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4140a4d15c21cd337a3c0b58ae8eeb64dbf47d3","tid":2217982,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c26da547958229c419d3c2cfba10840306805f1","tid":2217982,"uid":248299,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:34:52.000Z","msg":"咁先得果15k<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:47:28.000Z","msg":"on9 去集中營做咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706e4ef569d80c36332c75301e62b583918bab13","tid":2217982,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01